Create a reflector program 

install scapy() module:
git clone https://github.com/secdev/scapy.git
cd scapy
sudo python3 setup.py install

1. Read parameters from input as argument:
   - interface
   - victim-ip
   - victim-ethernet
   - reflector-ip
   - reflector-ethernet

2. call main()
3. use sniff function from scapy module and call function call_back in every packet 
4. in call_back function:
   if ARP packet -> call sendARPResponse
   if IP packet -> call sendIPResponse


